title: News Podcasts from ABC NewsRadio
text: Shon Walker presents But First - this week's weird and quirky stories that didn't make the headlines.On the menu this week:Even before the dust settles on the Orlando massacre, word comes of a U.S. state representative running a fund-raising raffle... with a rifle as the prize.The British Navy's in hot water... after their Billion Pound war-ships are stalling in the Persian Gulf because the water's too hot.And then there's the day that Facebook declared war on the Philippines.We've also got violence over food, a fight over a fart, and a wedding where the Priest punched out the groom's brother.There's also the chance to win your own newspaper... and we'll take you to a naked restaurant with very particular dress rules.This is the last ever episode of But First. So, for one last time let's go. Subscribe on iTunes Friday 17/06/2016
